div1.p:
United States District Court Western District of Washington Northern Division
In the Matter of the Application of Ng KwockKwack Kang for a Writ of Haveas Corpus
No. 3157 Order for Withdrawal of Exhibit
Upon the oral motion of the United States Attorney; It is hereby ordered that the government may permanently withdraw from the files of this cause its exhibit, consisting of the record of the Department of Labor Dated this 1st day of February, 1916.
Jeremiah Neterer United States District Judge
Recieved the above record this 1st day of February, 1916.
WK.John J. Sullivan

No. 3157 In the District Court of the United States for the Western District of Washington. Northern Division
In the Matter of the Application of Ng KwockKwack KanKang for a Writ of Habeas Corpus
Order for Withdrawal of Exhibit
Filed in the U.S. District Court Western Dist. of Washington, Northern Division Feb 1 - 1916 Frank L. Crosby, Clerk,
By EML Deputy
